These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: poker, domino, canasta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, writer, architect
City: miami, marseilles, boston
1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the architect##1
2. the police-officer is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person playing poker is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the architect is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Game         | domino | poker   | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Job   | architect  | police-officer    | writer      |
| City     | marseilles     | miami      | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, surfing, skateboarding
3 different games are played: go, chess, whist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia, poppy
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person playing whist##1
4. the person eating kale is the person playing chess##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Sport   | surfing     | skateboarding     | weightlifting      |
| Game   | whist  | chess | go |
| Flower           | poppy | dahlia     | zinnia       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, airplane
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, davidoff, siglo
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
House: modern, wooden, cottage
1. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the modern house is between the siglo-smoker and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
4. the wooden house is the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the modern house is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport          | taxi  | airplane     | snowmobile     |
| Cigar           | siglo | chaman  | davidoff   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| House           | cottage     | modern | wooden |

