.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, iced-tea
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, paramedic, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, adventure
3 different games are played: canasta, go, snooker
1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the paramedic and the person watching disaster movies##2
4. the person drinking juice is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage    | tea       | iced-tea  | juice   |
| Job     | paramedic    | scientist  | journalist |
| Movie-Genre     | animation   | adventure | disaster        |
| Game   | snooker | canasta     | go      |

