.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, balloon-flower
House: colonial, gothic-revival, craftsman
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, coffee
3 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the person drinking coffee and the craftsman house##2
3. the colonial house is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower          | balloon-flower    | poppy     | daffodil      |
| House         | colonial | gothic-revival | craftsman |
| Beverage   | coffee  | sprite       | lemonade       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

