.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, june, august
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bus, scooter
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, polish
1. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person driving the bus is between the person who's birthday is in june and the argentine##2
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Birthday          | june | july | august    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Transport   | subway   | bus     | scooter        |
| Nationality           | chinese      | polish       | argentine      |

