2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | almond-milk | cola     |
| Game          | monopoly   | chess      | backgammon     |
| Flower   | lily  | daisy      | dahlia |
| Birthday     | march | october        | may     |

