3. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of pop##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the victorian house##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
