3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, dannemann
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, snake
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person playing whist is between the dannemann-smoker and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Game           | canasta | whist        | poker       |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | swisher | dannemann |
| Pet           | snake     | pony         | guinea-pig  |
| Beverage         | juice  | soy-milk       | milk  |

