.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
City: marseilles, liverpool, miami
There 3 different types of food: garlic, lime, raspberry
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird, dog
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, colombian, argentine
1. the person traveling to miami is between the colombian and the person eating raspberry##2
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person eating garlic is the colombian##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| City      | liverpool    | miami          | marseilles |
| Food          | raspberry | lime           | garlic        |
| Pet           | bird | dog | chinchilla         |
| Nationality   | japanese    | argentine    | colombian      |

