3. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
4. the person eating cherry is between the dunhill-smoker and the person eating artichoke##2
5. the bolivar-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato  | cherry   | artichoke |
