3. the fan of electronic is the manager##1
4. the security-guard is the fan of disco##1
5. the person who growssunflower is the chef##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Birthday   | september    | march | december |
| Job           | manager        | security-guard   | chef  |
| Flower     | marigold      | zinnia   | sunflower |

