.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, apricot, ebony
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, october, march
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, soy-milk
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes ebony is between the person who likes grey and the person who's birthday is in october##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Color           | apricot   | ebony   | grey |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Birthday   | october     | december      | march    |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | fanta | soy-milk    |

