.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, water-polo, volleyball
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking
City: london, nizza, hamburg
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, balloon-flower, sunflower
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person traveling to london is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
4. the person traveling to nizza is the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person who growstulip is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person traveling to nizza##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | soccer | volleyball     | water-polo        |
| Hobby         | video-games   | woodworking | board-games |
| City   | nizza        | london       | hamburg      |
| Flower           | sunflower           | tulip    | balloon-flower       |

