.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, march, april
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda
House: gothic-revival, victorian, palace
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, tram
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the car##1
3. the victorian house is the person driving the car##1
4. the gothic-revival house is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is between the person driving the tram and the victorian house##2
6. the palace house is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Birthday        | march      | november | april |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate     | mirinda    | iced-tea        |
| House       | victorian | palace   | gothic-revival   |
| Transport   | car          | train     | tram       |

 